# EcoBuddy Home UI

This folder adds a static "Home" screen for the EcoBuddy app with the following features visible in the provided image:

- Daily Challenges (two checkboxes) — persistent per-day via localStorage
- Streak counter (increments when all daily challenges are completed for a day) with flame visual
- Did You Know info card
- EcoBuddy character rendered as inline SVG
- EcoBuddy Mood selector (happy / neutral / sad) with arrow and persistent selection
- "My accessories" button which opens a modal (placeholder for accessory management)
- Bottom navigation bar (Home, Add Task, My Friends, My Energy Stats, Settings) — buttons are present and wired to placeholder handlers

Open `ecobuddy-home/index.html` in a browser to run the demo locally.
